   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:03.03" end="00:00:05.36" region="speaker">This screen allows you to modify your response to</p>
         <p begin="00:00:05.36" end="00:00:07.93" region="speaker">the Disaster Recovery question.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:07.93" end="00:00:10.10" region="speaker">You will see a question asking whether or not you</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.10" end="00:00:12.46" region="speaker">agree to participate in the Recovery Purchasing</p>
         <p begin="00:00:12.46" end="00:00:13.63" region="speaker">Program.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:13.63" end="00:00:16.36" region="speaker">By selecting Yes, your company becomes eligible</p>
         <p begin="00:00:16.36" end="00:00:18.93" region="speaker">to receive orders made by state and local government</p>
         <p begin="00:00:18.93" end="00:00:21.53" region="speaker">entities to facilitate recovery from a major</p>
         <p begin="00:00:21.53" end="00:00:24.40" region="speaker">disaster or terrorism attack.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:24.40" end="00:00:27.76" region="speaker">Choose &quot;Yes&quot; or &quot;No.&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:27.76" end="00:00:29.16" region="speaker">When you finish, click &quot;Save and Continue.&quot;</p>
    </div>
